'''无畏印'''（[[梵语|梵语]]：'''Abhayamudrā'''），或称'''施无畏印'''，是[[印度宗教|印度宗教]]中常见的一种[[手印|手印]]，一般用来表示神圣力量的加护庇佑，使得众生感到信心、安全、无所畏怖。梵语'''abhaya'''意为“无畏”，来自否定前缀'''a-'''加上'''bhaya'''（“害怕、恐惧、怖畏”，词根为bhī）。<ref>{{cite book|editor1-last=Buswell|editor1-first=Robert Jr.|editor1-link=Robert Buswell Jr.|title=Princeton Dictionary of Buddhism.|date=2013|publisher=Princeton University Press|location=Princeton, NJ|isbn=9780691157863|page=2}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author1=Monier Monier-Williams |title=A Sanskrit-English Dictionary: Etymologically and Philologically Arranged with Special Reference to Cognate Indo-European Languages |publisher=Clarendon Press |location=Oxford |page=60 |url=https://www.sanskrit-lexicon.uni-koeln.de/scans/csl-apidev/servepdf.php?dict=MW&page=60 |accessdate=2022-01-19 |archive-date=2022-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119041104/https://www.sanskrit-lexicon.uni-koeln.de/scans/csl-apidev/servepdf.php?dict=MW&page=60 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author1=Monier Monier-Williams |title=A Sanskrit-English Dictionary: Etymologically and Philologically Arranged with Special Reference to Cognate Indo-European Languages |publisher=Clarendon Press |location=Oxford |page=747 |url=https://www.sanskrit-lexicon.uni-koeln.de/scans/csl-apidev/servepdf.php?dict=MW&page=747 |accessdate=2022-01-19 |archive-date=2022-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119041106/https://www.sanskrit-lexicon.uni-koeln.de/scans/csl-apidev/servepdf.php?dict=MW&page=747 }}</ref>其基本姿势为右手平举或抬起，手心朝外。<ref>{{cite web|title=Abhaya Mudra|url=http://www.religionfacts.com/buddhism/symbols/mudras/abhaya|date=2015-03-17|access-date=2015-02-10|archive-date=18 July 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150718014007/http://www.religionfacts.com/buddhism/symbols/mudras/abhaya|url-status=dead}}</ref>无畏印用于[[佛教|佛教]]、[[印度教|印度教]]、[[耆那教|耆那教]]及[[锡克教|锡克教]]等。在佛教中，施无畏印是[[五种印|五种印]]之一，另外四种为转法轮印、定印、证诚印及满愿印。<ref>{{cite web |title=五種印 |url=http://buddhism-dict.net/cgi-bin/xpr-ddb.pl?q=%E4%BA%94%E7%A8%AE%E5%8D%B0 |website=Digital Dictionary of Buddhism |accessdate=2022-01-19}}</ref>

[[File:Ahimsa_Jainism_Gradient.jpg|100px]]”（ahiṃsā）标志，手掌作无畏印]]
耆那教中的[[不害|不害]]（ahiṃsā）标志便是一只做施无畏印的手掌加上[[法轮|法轮]]。<ref>{{cite book |author1=Cain Carroll |title=Mudras of India: A Comprehensive Guide to the Hand Gestures of Yoga and Indian Dance |date=2013 |publisher=Singing Dragon |location=London |isbn=9781848191099 |pages=21-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Jain Hand (Ahimsa, Abhaya Mudra) |url=http://symboldictionary.net/?p=1834 |website=A Visual Glossary of Religious Symbols |accessdate=2022-01-19 |archive-date=2022-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119092401/http://symboldictionary.net/?p=1834 }}</ref>

